{"tid":316302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔做開group撚][足浴水療]召集所有喜愛足仔嘅巴打 8","createTime":"2017-07-10T15:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T09:28:36.000Z","uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93588aacc8c160b84cac5804827a446082fa7abd","tid":316302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"歡迎加入足仔嘅大家庭<br />\n新手有野問嘅話麻煩睇完介紹同Q&amp;A先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻煩所有未有經濟能力嘅人立即上一頁！<br />\n<br />\n最近各區都打風，長氣都要講多次，麻煩各位用暗號討論並加密，同時新手想問暗號之前請去望下Q&amp;A第8條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Q&amp;A打黎廢架？成篇根本係特登為你班自稱新手打，你唔睇亦都唔好怪巴打破口大罵</span><br />\n<br />\n注意 有鑑於近日發現有懷疑中學雞出入足浴場所，煩請各巴打討論時使用暗號表達鋪名，並加密，揚左出去大家都唔好受。同時請各巴打合作，如果見有人用5p字或人手filter問問題，請立即block，千奇唔好答佢問題，呢種人極有可能係中學生或者未有經濟能力。<br />\n<br />\n此外，開group撚請注意，呢個圈子已經好細，麻煩唔好係度自立門戶，多謝合作"},{"pid":"474f4b91905ceb587b1becd1efb956f49df838d4","tid":316302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77d8e8adee4e01bb889d2e11a2142c8c493754b","tid":316302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2544d626a7e0de7243406db0edcb50f58eb69954","tid":316302,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4bf37f488ced772e1b67b4ba72e7c6faf68a4437","tid":316302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7e9163e323cc8668fdf1243cfc1c608906e85c","tid":316302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"見冇人開所以我開<img src=\"/assets/faces/n